sprint_goal: Establish foundational vendor profile and product catalog CRUD functionality, enabling vendors to manually manage their storefront.
Implement core operational controls for vendors, including business hours, availability toggle, and the initial framework for license compliance.
Launch bulk catalog management features, including CSV import with error reporting, and enhance system compliance with automated license expiry reminders.
Deliver tools for the internal Onboarding Team to streamline vendor data migration and validation, and provide CSV export functionality for vendors.
